Ad.Title: Celly Later, says leading phone developer
Ad.Body: Recent mega-merger with Phony means big plus for consumers

In recent news, Celly just finished a mega-merger with rival cellphone company Phony. "We see this as a big plus for the consumer," says Bill Job, CEO and Founder. "Literally. Every cellphone will have a giant plus sign button on the front, and no other buttons. Simple, pure functionality."
